creator: 365LIVE INC.
descriptionHtml:
365Live brings you closer to exciting events, experiences, and entertainment. Whether you want to unwind at brunch, check out the local art scene, get tickets to live music or RSVP and hit the club, there is something fabulously fitting for everyone.
It doesn’t matter if you want to plan or do something last-minute. All you need to do is turn on your location and browse through the live or upcoming events in real-time. So, if you’re looking for things to do near you, while on vacation, or just happen to be traveling on the other side of the world, we offer a reliable resource of discovery—so that you can have a good time.
Features
Discover - Browse to find popular, private, and RSVP-only events near you without needing to sign up. Simply use location services or enter your location.
Booking – Book tickets, reserve seating, and secure your spot to all sorts of events. Or just browse free events at your convenience.
RSVP/Recommendation - Not only do we make it convenient to keep track and stay up-to-date with what’s happening around you based on what you like or enjoy doing, from time to time, we might receive invitations to popular events that may interest you. You can also RSVP to private events hosted by local organizers or friends.

Social - Our mission is to help you stay connected to the fun things you enjoy, so it’s only right we help you keep track of what your friends or colleagues might be attending and help you share the fun moments.
Tickets/Passes - All your tickets and past and upcoming bookings are always in a safe place for you. You can also add them to your wallet and share them with others.
